title: #92Noon! Friday Feast!
description: PA & Charch on a Friday, breaking down the playoff games with football talkers throughout. Pat Micheletti joins first hour to discuss the Wild's OT win last night in LA, Chad Greenway's weekly hangout, and Brian Baldinger analyzes the NFL games coming this weekend during the final hour!
